    "Table 16 shows the prompt used for our experiment with LLM judges.",
    "Prompt: Instruction Backtranslation/Reverse-engineering Assume the author of the provided text followed a detailed set of instructions to produce their work.",
    "Your task is to infer what those original instructions may have been by composing your own set of instructions that could recreate key aspects of the given text.",
